* [[World Transnational Open Teams Championship]] (1) 2000 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/transnational-open-teams.aspx World Transational Open Teams Winners]</ref>
* [[Rosenblum Cup]] (1) 2006 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-open-teams.aspx Rosenblum Cup Winners]</ref>
* [[Buffett Cup]] (2) 2010, 2012 
